::Zardus::

Zardus puts away his gun as Ominous flies off and the base defence stop 
firing. His last encounter with the bot wasn't this pleasant. He turns to 
Zergling.

"On second thought I'll stay at base. Continue your patrol," he says and 
walks back into the base.
